
report:
around 4 pages: 40% for system design, and 60% for evaluation

operations:
tar, gzip

Server Crash Recovery:
What does the server need to do to handle crashes properly?
What are points of danger during its operation?
what will happen if the server crashes at this point?
Will the server recover to an acceptable state?
Will the client get a service he expects?

Measurements:
How would you measure the performance of your system?
What aspects of the system should you measure?
Can you showcase its performance during normal operation, during server failure, the benefit of COMMITs, etc.?

